Hooks
-----

JSON POST to interface

Accepted upload
---------------

	{'accepted_upload: {
		'package': 'libfiu',
		'version': '0.23',
		'distribution': 'unstable',
		'urgency': 'high',
		'uploader': 'Chris Lamb <lamby@debian.org>',
		'closes': [12345, 12456, 146645],
	}}

Bug closed
----------

	{'bug_closed': {
		'number': 12637,
		'package': 'libfiu',
		'by': 'Chris Lamb <lamby@debian.org>',
		'title': 'hello',
	}}

